is de desporto, informa\u00e7\u00e3o, filmes e s\u00e9ries;\n\u2022 Ver conte\u00fados 360\u00ba atrav\u00e9s de uma experi\u00eancia totalmente imersiva.\n\nO MEO Go \u00e9 gr\u00e1tis para clientes com TV do MEO atrav\u00e9s da Internet de casa, consoante o pacote subscrito. Para aceder \u00e0s principais funcionalidades em qualquer liga\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0 Internet em Portugal, \u00e9 necess\u00e1rio subscrever o MEO Go Multi.\n\nTr\u00e1fego inclu\u00eddo na Rede M\u00f3vel MEO e nos hotspots MEO WiFi.\n\nPara utilizar a App MEO Go, fa\u00e7a login com os seus dados da \u00c1rea de Cliente. Se ainda n\u00e3o est\u00e1 registado, aceda a meogo.pt.", "short_description": "Experimente tamb\u00e9m o MEO Go em realidade virtual para ver TV em direto e conte\u00fados 360\u00ba numa experi\u00eancia totalmente imersiva."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.meo.pt/politica-de-privacidade", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://conteudos.meo.pt/meo/Documentos/Condicoes-Adesao/Condicoes-Adesao-servicos-comunicacoes-eletronicas-MEO-Mod-C1000600.pdf", "publisher_name": "MEO - Servi\u00e7os de Comunica\u00e7\u00f5es, S.A.", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://meogo.pt/", "category": "ENTERTAINMENT", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["MOVIE", "EXPLORATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["pt"], "supported_input_devices": [], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "505872081124696"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 0, "nodes": []}, "baseline_offer": null, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": []}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {